                },
                "message": "Improve handling on non-heaptype bases on Py3.9 Limited API\n\n1. Fixes an issue in `__Pyx_MergeVtables` where accessing the\n   final `object` base fails because it isn't a heap-type.\n2. Raise an error in the constructor for a type than cannot be\n   instantiated because we can't reach its base.\n\nThis will affect inheritance from external types.",
